(firstQuint)Long-Term Study of Multi-target Therapy as Maintenance Treatment for Lupus Nephritis.

 Azathioprine (AZA) has been used for maintenance therapy of lupus nephritis for many years.

 We compare the efficacy and safety of multi-target therapy as continuous induction and maintenance treatment vs CTX-Aza.

